{"tid":1173628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門酒店嘆A級和牛要求半生熟　食客「大開眼界」：一面熟一面生","createTime":"2019-05-27T08:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T13:26:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b59ca438ed0c8d2377d459fde03642f1f8c34572","tid":1173628,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359508/steak_thumb_20190527_J_v2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359508%2Fsteak_thumb_20190527_J_v2_600.jpg&h=155e3a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多人食牛扒都愛半生熟，但一面熟、一面生的牛扒大家又見過未？日前有網民不滿澳門某酒店餐廳的食物質素，廚師竟烹調一塊「煎一面熟、一面生」的牛扒，於是上載照片至飲食group投訴。<br />\n<br />\n有網民日前上載3張照片至facebook「澳門難食中伏團」，投訴某間酒店餐廳的自助晚餐質素差。發帖者指，初時覺得自助餐價錢「幾抵」，用餐時亦覺得食物「味道OK」，但補充食物的速度慢，長腳蟹不新鮮，其中主菜餐牌「席切A级和牛」及「威靈頓酥皮牛柳」推出一次後已沒有再補充食物，隨後再推出的牛扒據發帖者形容都是「全熟」、「鞋口」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後發帖者向廚師詢問：<br />\n<br />\n「可唔可以煎塊半熟的？」<br />\n<br />\n結果廚師真的煎了一塊一面熟、一面生的牛扒。發帖者形容「咁嘅服務態度第一次見」、「去唔去食真係自己諗，俾錢買氣受」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文上載群組後網民瘋傳，網民笑言廚師烹調技巧高超、有創意，不少網民都笑指廚師沒有錯：<br />\n<br />\n「無錯喎，5成熟，一半熟，一半唔熟，啱啊，哈哈哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n亦有人稱可能廚師忙中有錯「牛排忘記反面煎了」。<br />\n<br />\n網民根據餐牌發現事件中的餐廳為澳門一間三星級酒店，而發帖者相片中的「最牛自助晚餐精裝牌」餐牌亦於該酒店的Facebook上可見。有網民將帖文截圖並上載至酒店Facebook要求解釋。<br />\n<br />\nTOPick就事件致電餐廳查詢，職員表示正了解事件並會作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2359508/澳門酒店嘆A級和牛要求半生熟%E3%80%80食客「大開眼界」：一面熟一面生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2359508%2F%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%98%86A%E7%B4%9A%E5%92%8C%E7%89%9B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8D%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%86%9F%25E3%2580%2580%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%8B%E7%9C%BC%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E7%86%9F%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E7%94%9F&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWOojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=e84894c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2359508/澳門酒店嘆A級和牛要求半生熟%E3%80%80食客「大開眼界」：一面熟一面生</a>"},{"pid":"e3dc933144fc601cc06d3f021109fd5c83149202","tid":1173628,"uid":144843,"like":246,"dislike":1,"score":245,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c7f8663008bff2b17ab03b2d1827db77cfd30c7","tid":1173628,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":65,"score":-64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"傻眼"},{"pid":"29a0c5c023d8e44877db172a247d35b8d12142ba","tid":1173628,"uid":76776,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdad9e882cbe9a99982904e1c28d9b13dd3da59a","tid":1173628,"uid":83907,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"肯定係個客閪"},{"pid":"c98605e9e1824ac95f272c80d0e31a9861884db1","tid":1173628,"uid":46277,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"50% = (100% + 0%)/2 = (well done + rare )/2 = medium steak <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e1b526050b53b736745607cf09b5dba97d8ad3","tid":1173628,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"睇塊扒笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a9724aabcdec1814dc4966ce126dc5def33ef4","tid":1173628,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"原來係馬交"},{"pid":"da38090657da1ea8713867a5c8a8a11ffb4ba07f","tid":1173628,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"咁幽默啊廚房佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8315f4101d07ccaba4db3f92711aa96a62a5fee2","tid":1173628,"uid":26752,"like":51